Jaakon Git v1.0.4.0

Syntax highlighting
- A small bunch of programming languages supported
- A default highlight scheme that works reasonably well with any unsupported
  language
- User can define their own highlight schemes
- Can be disabled in Settings

Auto-refresh
- Working tree status (staging area) refreshed automatically when application
  is brought to foreground
- Can be disabled in Settings

Bug fixes
- Crash when editing diff of a file that no longer exists

